app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/2076-0817/9/4/310/s1, Table S1: Updates concerning important mosquito borne diseases. We listed most of the mosquito-borne diseases, including their actual distribution, transmission, natural occurrence or animal infection, and virulence as well as the existence or absence of treatments or vaccines to date.
